4868 payload->external_port = htobe16(payload->external_port);
4869 payload->external_sw_if_index = htobe32(payload->external_sw_if_index);
4870 payload->vrf_id = htobe32(payload->vrf_id);
4871}

4876 payload->external_port = be16toh(payload->external_port);

8236 if (VAPI_OK != vapi_producer_unlock (ctx)) {
8237 abort (); /* this really shouldn't happen */
8238 }
8239 if (vapi_is_nonblocking(ctx)) {
8240 rv = VAPI_OK;
8241 } else {
8242 rv = vapi_dispatch(ctx);
8243 }
8244 } else {
8245 vapi_msg_nat44_forwarding_enable_disable_ntoh(msg);
8246 if (VAPI_OK != vapi_producer_unlock (ctx)) {
8247 abort (); /* this really shouldn't happen */
8248 }
8249 }
8250 return rv;
8251}
